HEADWORD: kowhai
<hw>kowhai</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A shrub or small tree (<spn>Sophora
tetraptera</spn>) of New Zealand and Chile having pendulous racemes of
tubular golden-yellow flowers; it yields a hard strong wood.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> <spn>Sophora tetraptera</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

